            section.py-5
                .container
                    .row
                        .col-md-6.my-auto
                            div(style="display: flex; align-items: center")
                                img(src="images/logo.png" width=60 style="vertical-align:middle; margin: 0px 10px 0px 0px")
                                h1.display-4(id="download") Intrepid
                            p.lead.text-muted.mb-4 Free and open source note-taking app for macOS, built on the Chronicle file format.
                            a.btn.btn-primary(href="https://github.com/sarimabbas/intrepid/releases/latest") Download alpha for free
                            a.btn.btn-link(href="https://github.com/sarimabbas/intrepid") View on GitHub
                        .col-md-6
                            img.img-fluid.mt-4.mt-md-0(src="images/Screen_Shot_2019-11-27_at_4.26.37_PM.png", alt="")

            section.py-5
                .container
                    h2.mb-5.text-center(id="features") Features
                    .row
                        .col-md-4.mb-4
                            .card
                                img.card-img-top(src="images/asset.png", alt="Asset management")
                                .card-body
                                    h5.card-title Asset management
                                    p It's all Markdown but the Chronicle <code>.crncl</code> file format bundles all images and assets to make sharing files convenient.

                        .col-md-4.mb-4
                            .card
                                img.card-img-top(src="images/outline.png", alt="Outline view")
                                .card-body
                                    h5.card-title Outline thoughts
                                    p The sidebar is populated from your heading structure and lets you quickly jump around the document.
                        .col-md-4.mb-4
                            .card
                                img.card-img-top(src="images/smart.png", alt="Smart blocks")
                                .card-body
                                    h5.card-title Smart blocks
                                    p Embed YouTube videos, bookmark any link to see rich previews and write KaTeX math.

